Installation Instructions
=========================

Linux
=====

First, configure the build:

  $ meson setup build/

Start the build with:

  $ meson compile -C build/

And install DirectFB-examples using:

  $ meson install -C build/

NuttX
=====

On NuttX, copy the DirectFB-examples directory to your NuttX apps/examples/ directory, renaming it DirectFB.
